    ["Changes"] = {
        { "Title", "\240\159\143\134 RANKED" },
        { "Description", "Welcome to Ranked Season 0!" },
        { "Description", "This season will be the first ever look at the new Ranked mode." },
        { "Description", "Everything is subject to change and we welcome all feedback and criticism as we improve Ranked to make it the most competitive experience on Roblox!" },
        { "Header", "How to play Ranked" },
        { "Description", "Ranked is the brand new, competitive mode in RIVALS! You can compete against other players in a stricter, fairer environment to see who\'s the best!" },
        { "Description", "To unlock access to Ranked, simply open up the Ranked page by first pressing the Play button or by interacting with the Ranked Hologram in the lobby!" },
        { "Description", "There, you will either have immediate access to Ranked or have to complete a few requirements before gaining access." },
        { "Header", "Unlocking your rank" },
        { "Description", "Once Ranked is unlocked, you can start playing your first few Ranked duels. These initial set of duels are known as your \"placements\"." },
        { "Description", "Your placements are 10 duels long. Once you play 10 Ranked duels, you will unlock your starting rank!" },
        { "Description", "Once your rank is unlocked, any further Ranked duels will result in gaining / losing ELO!" },
        { "Header", "What is ELO?" },
        { "Description", "ELO is what determines your rank. The more ELO you have, the higher your rank is. Better players have more ELO!" },
        { "Description", "Losing a Ranked duel lowers your ELO, while winning a Ranked duel raises your ELO!" },
        { "Description", "Once you\'ve gained enough ELO, you will promote to a better rank!" },
        { "Description", "Likewise, if you happen to lose enough ELO, you will unfortunately demote to a lower rank." },
        { "Description", "ELO can only be affected by playing Ranked \226\128\148 your ELO is completely safe in all other modes!" },
        { "Description", "After your placements are complete, you will start to receive 1 free ELO Shield every day. This protects you from losing ELO for 1 Ranked duel! ELO Shields cannot be purchased or earned in any other way." },
        { "Header", "What\'s different in Ranked?" },
        { "Description", "Ranked duels have a variety of gameplay changes & restrictions." },
        { "Description", "Map pools are kept fair & competitive, which means maps such as Backrooms will not show up during voting!" },
        { "Description", "During voting, only 3 maps will be shown at a time. Both teams will then get to ban 1 of these maps, leaving 1 map remaining!" },
        { "Description", "Once map bans are complete, both teams will then start banning weapons. This completely disables a weapon for the entire duel!" },
        { "Description", "Mobile & controller handicaps are restricted in Ranked. Third Person Mode is disabled, Aim Assist Strength is capped at 50%, and Auto Shoot Mode is restricted to Dynamic \226\128\148 a new feature that keeps problematic weapons in check!" },
        { "Description", "Last but not least, Weapon Switching is restricted to only 2 switches max for the entire duel!" },
        { "Description", "Win streaks are safe in Ranked!" },
        { "Header", "Ranked rewards" },
        { "Description", "Throughout the season, you are able to earn a free Common Skin \226\128\148 the Phoenix Rifle! This Assault Rifle skin is obtained simply by winning enough ranked duels \226\128\148 more details in the Ranked page!" },
        { "Description", "There will be end-of-season rewards based on your final ELO & total ranked wins \226\128\148 soon to be announced!" },
        { "Header", "Leaderboard" },
        { "Description", "There\'s a brand new leaderboard just for Ranked!" },
        { "Description", "This leaderboard stands alone in the hallway to the duel pads. Here, you can see the top players in the world!" },
        { "Description", "Players that place high on this leaderboard will be rewarded with extremely rare & exclusive loot at the end of the season \226\128\148 soon to be announced!" },
        { "Title", "\240\159\151\186 MAPS" },
        { "Description", "Brand new lobby created by @GreatGuyBoom!" },
        { "Description", "NEW \"Playground\" Map \226\128\148 Created by @Nosniy!" },
        { "Description", "NEW \"Big Onyx\" Map \226\128\148 Created by @ShadowTrojan!" },
        { "Description", "REVAMPED \"Onyx\" Map \226\128\148 Created by @ShadowTrojan!" },
        { "Description", "REVAMPED \"Docks\" Map \226\128\148 Created by @Nosniy!" },
        { "Description", "REVAMPED \"Splash\" Map \226\128\148 Created by @Nosniy!" },
        { "Description", "REVAMPED \"Big Splash\" Map \226\128\148 Created by @Nosniy!" },
        { "Description", "NEW Legacy Maps \226\128\148 You can now play all of the legacy versions of existing maps in Private Servers which includes Legacy Backrooms, Legacy Big Splash, Legacy Splash, Legacy Docks, Legacy Onyx, & Legacy Big Crossroads!" },
        { "Description", "Slight visual improvements to Station!" },
        { "Description", "Several maps now use the new out-of-bounds feature from Bridge to ensure a fun experience on all maps!" },
