        { "Description", "New Maps page in the Career page \226\128\148 Shows you all of the maps in the game & who made them, which queues they can be played in, and your performance on each map! NOTE: Your map performances have begun tracking now and are only accurate starting from this update onwards!" },
        { "Title", "\226\173\144 GAMEPLAY" },
        { "Description", "Players now receive a 0.5s forcefield at the start of rounds!" },
