        { "Description", "You can no longer draw rounds on purpose!" },
        { "Description", "Almost every weapon has received balance changes! Handicaps for mobile & controller players have also been addressed! View all of the details below in \"\240\159\148\171 BALANCE CHANGES\"!" },
