        { "Description", "Brand new animations for the Hot Coals skin!" },
        { "Title", "\226\154\153 SETTINGS" },
        { "Description", "New Crosshair Setting \"Show While Aiming\" \226\128\148 Makes it so that your crosshair doesn\'t disappear while aiming with a weapon!" },
        { "Description", "New Crosshair Setting \"Scale\" \226\128\148 Allows you to easily grow & shrink your crosshair!" },
        { "Description", "New Crosshair Settings \"Circle\" \226\128\148 A new crosshair component that places a circle around your center dot!" },
        { "Description", "New Setting \"Aiming Hides Muzzle Flash\" \226\128\148 Turning this on will completely hide muzzle flash effects while aiming with a weapon!" },
        { "Description", "New Setting \"Auto Shoot Mode\" \226\128\148 Allows you to use Dynamic mode which means your Auto Shoot\'s reaction time will dynamically change based on the weapon you\'re using! This setting is enforced in Ranked and exists here to allow players to practice for Ranked!" },
        { "Description", "New Setting \"Auto Shoot Reaction Time\" \226\128\148 You can now change your Auto Shoot\'s reaction time (in milliseconds) to whatever you prefer so long as \"Auto Shoot Mode\" is set to Enabled!" },
        { "Title", "\226\154\148 PRIVATE SERVERS" },
