        { "Description", "You now have to manually enable the \"Unrestricted Map Voting\" setting in a Private Server to gain access to all maps in private duels!" },
        { "Title", "\240\159\148\171 BALANCE CHANGES" },
        { "Header", "Bow" },
        { "Description", "\240\159\147\157 \"These changes aim to make Bow less of a spam weapon\"" },
        { "Description", "\240\159\148\187 Damage decreased from 40 \226\134\146 30" },
        { "Description", "\240\159\148\187 Critical damage decreased from 60 \226\134\146 50" },
        { "Description", "\240\159\146\170 Charge damage increased from (50% / 100% / 150% / 200%) \226\134\146 (50% / 100% / 150% / 240%)" },
        { "Description", "\240\159\146\170 Move Speed increased from Normal \226\134\146 +5%" },
        { "Header", "Crossbow" },
        { "Description", "\240\159\147\157 \"The previous nerfs for Crossbow were too harsh\"" },
        { "Description", "\240\159\146\170 Damage increased from 37.5 \226\134\146 45" },
        { "Description", "\226\158\150 Critical hit multiplier decreased from 2x \226\134\146 1.667x" },
        { "Header", "RPG" },
        { "Description", "\240\159\147\157 \"The RPG struggled to be viable with a 4-hit-elimination, so it\'s getting some power shifted to it\'s splash damage\"" },
        { "Description", "\240\159\146\170 Splash damage increased from 40 \226\134\146 50" },
        { "Description", "\240\159\148\187 Direct damage decreased from 120 \226\134\146 100" },
        { "Header", "Shotgun" },
        { "Description", "\240\159\147\157 \"These changes will help shotgun feel more consistent\"" },
        { "Description", "\240\159\146\170 New consistent spread" },
        { "Description", "\240\159\146\170 Bullets can now pierce through multiple enemies" },
        { "Description", "\240\159\148\187 Shoot cooldown increased from 0.7s \226\134\146 0.8s" },
        { "Header", "Energy Rifle" },
        { "Description", "\240\159\147\157 \"This rework makes the Energy Rifle\'s bounce shots more practical to use and less gimmicky\"" },
        { "Description", "\240\159\148\187 Bounce body shots no longer deal critical damage" },
        { "Description", "\240\159\148\187 Damage decreased from 20 \226\134\146 15" },
        { "Description", "\240\159\148\187 Critical damage decreased from 60 \226\134\146 25" },
        { "Description", "\240\159\146\170 Direct headshots can now deal critical damage" },
        { "Description", "\240\159\146\170 Bounce Redirection Angle increased from 0\194\176 \226\134\146 10\194\176" },
        { "Header", "Flamethrower" },
        { "Description", "\240\159\147\157 \"Burn weapons have been collectively standardized\"" },
        { "Description", "\240\159\148\187 Airblast can now only push smoke clouds instead of clearing them" },
        { "Description", "\240\159\148\187 Burn damage has been reworked, view note at the bottom of the balance changes for more detail" },
        { "Description", "\240\159\148\187 Total DPS decreased by ~25%" },
        { "Header", "Grenade Launcher" },
        { "Description", "\240\159\147\157 \"Bringing down the direct damage prevents certain weapon combos from dominating. We also want the projectile hitbox to feel similar to the RPG\"" },
        { "Description", "\240\159\146\170 Projectile hitbox size increased from 0.5studs \226\134\146 1stud" },
        { "Description", "\240\159\148\187 Direct damage decreased from 100 \226\134\146 80" },
        { "Header", "Gunblade" },
        { "Description", "\240\159\147\157 \"We\'re improving the Gunblade\'s performance to compete with meta primaries\"" },
        { "Description", "\240\159\146\170 Move Speed increased from -10% \226\134\146 Normal" },
        { "Description", "\240\159\146\170 Damage dropoff has been removed" },
        { "Description", "\240\159\148\187 Max Ammo decreased from 16 \226\134\146 8" },
        { "Header", "Minigun" },
        { "Description", "\240\159\147\157 \"Minigun has been a quiet menace. We\'ll be keeping an eye on it\'s performance after these slight nerfs\"" },
        { "Description", "\240\159\148\187 Critical hit multiplier decreased from 1.5x \226\134\146 1.25x" },
        { "Description", "\240\159\148\187 Damage dropoff minimum distance decreased from 100studs \226\134\146 50studs" },
        { "Header", "Paintball Gun" },
        { "Description", "\240\159\147\157 \"This rework aims to make the Paintball Gun feel more like real paintball guns in the sense of having lots of ammo\"" },
        { "Description", "\240\159\146\170 Max Ammo increased from 16 \226\134\146 24" },
        { "Description", "\240\159\148\187 Max Ammo Reserve decreased from 48 \226\134\146 24" },
        { "Description", "\240\159\148\187 Damage decreased from 20 \226\134\146 18.5" },
        { "Header", "Daggers" },
        { "Description", "\240\159\147\157 \"Daggers have felt too much like a primary weapon\"" },
        { "Description", "\240\159\148\187 Damage decreased from 20 \226\134\146 15" },
        { "Description", "\240\159\148\187 Move Speed decreased from +15% \226\134\146 +5%" },
        { "Header", "Energy Pistols" },
        { "Description", "\240\159\147\157 \"While the Energy Pistols trade strength for unlimited ammo and speed, it proved to be too weak\"" },
        { "Description", "\240\159\146\170 Damage increased from 2.25 \226\134\146 2.4" },
        { "Header", "Flare Gun" },
        { "Description", "\240\159\147\157 \"Burn weapons have been collectively standardized\"" },
        { "Description", "\240\159\148\187 Flares are now colored properly to indicate danger" },
        { "Description", "\240\159\148\187 Burn damage has been reworked, view note at the bottom of the balance changes for more detail" },
        { "Description", "\240\159\148\187 Total DPS decreased by ~50%" },
        { "Header", "Handgun" },
        { "Description", "\240\159\147\157 \"This change conserves the Handgun\'s power while requiring less spam-clicking to make use of it\"" },
        { "Description", "\240\159\146\170 Equip cooldown decreased from 0.66s \226\134\146 0.45s" },
        { "Description", "\240\159\146\170 Damage increased from 11 \226\134\146 13" },
        { "Description", "\240\159\148\187 Shoot Cooldown increased from 0.1s \226\134\146 0.13s" },
        { "Header", "Shorty" },
        { "Description", "\240\159\147\157 \"The Shorty is going to keep its lethal damage in exchange for a significant ammo reduction\"" },
        { "Description", "\240\159\146\170 New consistent spread" },
        { "Description", "\240\159\148\187 Spread increased from 10\194\176 \226\134\146 15\194\176" },
        { "Description", "\240\159\148\187 Max Ammo Reserve decreased from 36 \226\134\146 2" },
        { "Header", "Slingshot" },
        { "Description", "\240\159\147\157 \"Slingshot has been extremely oppressive and way too powerful for a secondary weapon\"" },
        { "Description", "\240\159\148\187 Damage decreased from 7 \226\134\146 6" },
        { "Description", "\240\159\148\187 Can no longer deal critical damage" },
        { "Description", "\240\159\148\187 Move Speed decreased from +10% \226\134\146 +5%" },
        { "Header", "Spray" },
        { "Description", "\240\159\147\157 \"The Spray has struggled to find an identity \226\128\148 we now want it to be the cheap counter to Katanas & Riot Shields\"" },
        { "Description", "\240\159\146\170 Equip cooldown decreased from 1s \226\134\146 0.45s" },
        { "Description", "\240\159\146\170 Now uses illegally-modified-armor-piercing-rounds that can penetrate through shields & deflects" },
        { "Description", "\240\159\146\170 Move Speed increased from Normal \226\134\146 +5%" },
        { "Description", "\240\159\151\157 Price has been reduced from 25 keys \226\134\146 5 keys" },
        { "Header", "Uzi" },
        { "Description", "\240\159\147\157 \"This quality of life change makes the Uzi feel better to use\"" },
        { "Description", "\240\159\146\170 Aim Speed increased from 100% \226\134\146 150%" },
        { "Header", "Battle Axe" },
        { "Description", "\240\159\147\157 \"The high spin damage created too many anti-fun strategies\"" },
        { "Description", "\240\159\148\187 Spin Damage decreased from 50 \226\134\146 40" },
        { "Description", "\240\159\146\170 Damage increased from 50 \226\134\146 55" },
        { "Header", "Trowel" },
        { "Description", "\240\159\147\157 \"We\'re improving the Trowel\'s cover-on-demand identity in addition to reducing the effectiveness of barricading on certain maps\"" },
        { "Description", "\240\159\146\170 Wall hitboxes now build instantly (visuals have stayed the same)" },
        { "Description", "\240\159\148\187 Wall Max Bricks decreased from 75 \226\134\146 25" },
        { "Description", "\240\159\148\187 Hardened Bricks can no longer be re-thrown" },
        { "Header", "Flashbang" },
        { "Description", "\240\159\147\157 \"We\'re removing this unintended & toxic mechanic\"" },
        { "Description", "\240\159\148\187 Can no longer be cooked" },
        { "Header", "Freeze Ray" },
        { "Description", "\240\159\147\157 \"All actions should be halted while frozen for consistency purposes\"" },
        { "Description", "\240\159\146\170 Enemies can no longer switch weapons while frozen" },
        { "Header", "Molotov" },
        { "Description", "\240\159\147\157 \"Burn weapons have been collectively standardized\"" },
        { "Description", "\240\159\146\170 Splash damage increased from 0 \226\134\146 10" },
        { "Description", "\240\159\146\170 Hitboxes are now extremely consistent" },
        { "Description", "\240\159\148\187 Fire can no longer spawn through walls" },
        { "Description", "\240\159\148\187 Burn damage has been reworked, view note at the bottom of the balance changes for more detail" },
        { "Description", "\240\159\148\187 Total DPS decreased by ~33%" },
        { "Header", "Satchel" },
        { "Description", "\240\159\147\157 \"Satchel was ridiculously powerful on launch. We\'re swapping its power for mobility, while also rewarding strategic placements\"" },
        { "Description", "\240\159\148\187 Damage decreased from 50 \226\134\146 20" },
        { "Description", "\240\159\148\187 Can no longer stick onto teammates that don\'t have Riot Shields" },
        { "Description", "\240\159\146\170 Satchels attached to walls now deal critical damage" },
        { "Description", "\240\159\146\170 Knockback increased from 125% \226\134\146 150%" },
        { "Header", "Smoke Grenade" },
        { "Description", "\240\159\147\157 \"It doesn\'t make sense for smoke clouds to last long in fast-paced duels\"" },
        { "Description", "\240\159\148\187 Smoke cloud lifetime decreased from 30s \226\134\146 10s" },
        { "Header", "Other" },
        { "Description", "\240\159\148\187 3rd Person Camera removed from controller players" },
        { "Description", "\240\159\146\170 Mobile players can now sprint & slide while aiming with a weapon" },
        { "Description", "\240\159\146\170 Auto Shoot no longer activates if the enemy is out-of-reach for weapons like Flamethrower & melees" },
        { "Description", "\240\159\148\187 Auto Shoot can no longer shoot enemies that are behind you while in 3rd person" },
        { "Description", "\240\159\148\187 Aim Assist has been reworked to have a more springy-feel which may be harder to control" },
        { "Description", "\240\159\148\187 Burn damage no longer deals damage the moment it\'s applied to a player. This used to cause scenarios where fire weapons would deal ~25-50% more damage than intended as the burn would kick in instantly. This behavior also allowed multiple fire weapons to deal unintentionally high amounts of damage when paired together. This change not only makes fire weapons more fair to play against, but also makes it easier for the developers to balance these mechanics." },
        { "Title", "\240\159\155\160 OTHER" },
        { "Description", "You can now bind the same keybind to multiple different actions (example: MB1 can be used to both Aim & Shoot)" },
        { "Description", "Teammates are now transparent at round start" },
        { "Description", "Slight visual improvements to the Elimination Feed interface" },
        { "Description", "Slight visual improvements to the Settings page" },
        { "Description", "Slight visual improvements to the Party interface" },
        { "Description", "Slight visual improvements to the Final Results interface" },
        { "Description", "New player card UI after a duel ends" },
