        { "Description", "The bottom button for the Career page has been removed and can now be accessed by first going into the Weapons page" },
        { "Description", "The bottom button for the Rewards page has been removed and can now be accessed by first going into the Shop page" },
        { "Description", "The Festive Event has concluded and all associated limited time content & cosmetics are no longer available" },
        { "Description", "Unlock Tokens have been converted into Standard Weapon Crates & are now completely discontinued" },
        { "Title", "\240\159\144\155 BUG FIXES" },
        { "Description", "Fixed a bug where using a Medkit would give you a cooldown even if it didn\'t end up healing you" },
        { "Description", "Fixed a bug where Auto Shoot wouldn\'t properly throw Grenades & other similar weapons" },
        { "Description", "Fixed a bug that allowed players to fling Molotovs far away super quickly" },
        { "Description", "Fixed a rare bug with Scythe that allowed players to hop at ridiculous speeds" },
        { "Description", "Fixed a dash-jump bug with Scythe/Battle Axe/Gunblade & Subspace Tripmine" },
        { "Description", "Fixed a rare bug where flares would be invisible but still deal damage to players" },
        { "Description", "Fixed a bug where smoke clouds sometimes wouldnt extinguish flares" },
        { "Description", "Fixed a bug where Smoke Grenades and Molotovs would activate when going through invisible barriers" },
        { "Description", "Fixed a bug with Chainsaw / Flamethrower where being frozen wouldn\'t cancel your inputs" },
        { "Description", "Fixed an audio bug with Satchel detonate" },
        { "Description", "Fixed a bug where the Milk & Cookies healing animation healed you slightly sooner than intended" },
        { "Description", "Fixed various UI bugs where certain UI elements would clash with other UI elements" },
        { "Description", "Fixed a bug where the mobile controls editor showed up for non-mobile players when hiding the HUD" },
        { "Description", "Fixed a bug where locked cosmetics wouldn\'t appear to be locked when viewing lootbox contents" },
        { "Description", "Fixed a bug where owned weapons wouldn\'t appear to be owned when viewing lootbox contents" },
        { "Description", "Fixed a bug where you couldn\'t import mobile controls from another player" },
        { "Description", "Fixed a bug that caused the on-screen-keyboard to get stuck for mobile players while chatting during the teleport screen" },
        { "Description", "Fixed a rare bug where players using a controller showed up as if they were playing on keyboard & mouse" },
        { "Description", "Fixed a bug that caused DPS dummies to display slightly inaccurate DPS" },
        { "Description", "Fixed a rare bug where changing the jump keybind wouldn\'t work" },
        { "Description", "Fixed a rare bug where you would randomly spectate other players during a duel even while you\'re alive" },
        { "Description", "Fixed a bug where spectating an empty duel would spectate the lobby instead of the map" },
        { "Description", "Fixed a bug where match point / sudden death in Graveyard / Big Graveyard wouldn\'t change the lighting properly" },
        { "Description", "Fixed a bug in Construction where the spinning shipping container could be messed up by specific weapons" },
        { "Description", "Fixed a bug where disabling textures didn\'t affect maps like Crossroads/Big Crossroads" },
        { "Description", "Fixed a bug where disabling textures mid-game wouldn\'t do anything" },
        { "Description", "Fixed a bug that caused some players to be put into games even after stepping off of a queue pad" },
        { "Description", "Fixed a bug where slide jumping into a thin wall allowed you to noclip through it" },
        { "Description", "Fixed a bug where players would spawn underneath the floor and/or inside of walls in certain maps" },
        { "Description", "Potentially fixed a bug that caused players to float away at the start of rounds" },
        { "Description", "Fixed a visual bug with how crosshair outlines overlapped" },
        { "Description", "Fixed bugs in all maps where certain spots wouldn\'t cause explosive projectiles to detonate" },
        { "Description", "Fixed invisible barriers in all maps" },
        { "Description", "Fixed a bug in Graveyard where windows couldn\'t be broken" },
        { "Title", "\240\159\147\156 A NOTE FROM THE DEVELOPERS" },
        { "Description", "We hope you all enjoy Ranked! It\'s been a long time coming and we\'ve worked very hard to get this out as soon as possible to everyone." },
        { "Description", "This is our first time working on something like this and we\'re excited to see how the ranked scene unfolds!" },
        { "Description", "We will be taking any and all feedback very seriously as we understand how important it is to listen to the community when it comes to competitive scenes." },
        { "Description", "There may or may not be a few issues right now with Ranked that we may have overlooked or not anticipated for, but rest assured that we\'re committed to fixing & improving everything we can in a timely manner." },
